item.title: Compile Error please help Vistex v7
item.dc:creator: @InvisionX InvisionX
item.description:
@InvisionX wrote:

replace that statement in the clanchathandler at your source folder with this
c.getPA().sendFrame126("Talking in: " + clans[clanId].name, 18139);
c.getPA().sendFrame126("Owner: " + clans[clanId].owner, 18140);
and it should work
